{"author":"Iso Tester","data":{"alias":"toy-kink-ire","description":"## Context\n\nB-RETIRE removed bespoke orchestrator.run_review, which was the ONLY producer of the per-pass latency/cost metrics (db7b AC5: coverage['metrics'] = {det_ms, llm_ms, total_ms, llm_calls, claim_path}). The workflow plan-review path does not emit them, so coverage['metrics'] is now absent on the workflow gate (the sidecar emits {}). This is a passive-observability regression (the metrics fed passive latency/cost-target refinement from dogfood data).\n\n## Acceptance Criteria\n\n- [ ] The workflow plan-review path emits coverage['metrics'] (det_ms / llm_ms / total_ms / llm_calls) equivalent to the retired run_review telemetry, captured from the workflow run (recorder step timings / the batch_plan coverage).\n- [ ] The sidecar carries the metrics again on the workflow gate.\n- [ ] A test asserts metrics are produced on the workflow path.","id":"4a40-ea6e-d3f7-4af7","parent_id":"72d5-79ec-9e2e-4a2b","priority":2,"tags":[],"ticket_type":"task","title":"Reinstate per-pass latency/cost telemetry (coverage.metrics) on the workflow plan-review gate"},"env_id":"ade0f2ef-51cc-45a2-bb97-c09846cd3df5","event_type":"CREATE","timestamp":1782523751460216001,"uuid":"806e9408-f5e7-4ba0-bc9c-c14d498807af"}